154
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,633
<c.Japanese>あっ</c.Japanese>

155
00:07:43,433 --> 00:07:44,533
<c.Japanese>あっ！</c.Japanese>

156
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:49,066
