332
00:15:36,833 --> 00:15:39,366
<c.Japanese>ここに目指すものがあるはずだ</c.Japanese>

333
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:40,100
<c.Japanese>探せ</c.Japanese>

334
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:42,000
<c.Japanese>（狩屋）はい</c.Japanese>

335
00:15:54,466 --> 00:15:55,066
<c.Japanese>何を？</c.Japanese>

336
00:15:56,533 --> 00:15:57,800
<c.Japanese>（エリカ）“おじさん”？</c.Japanese>

337
00:15:58,800 --> 00:15:59,333
<c.Japanese>（貝原）え？</c.Japanese>

338
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,766
<c.Japanese>いや 大学のオタクたちにね<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

339
