340
00:16:03,833 --> 00:16:05,100
<c.Japanese>ダメだ これ</c.Japanese>

341
00:16:05,433 --> 00:16:06,900
<c.Japanese>（蔵本）ン〜</c.Japanese>

342
00:16:07,133 --> 00:16:08,500
<c.Japanese>任せなさい</c.Japanese>

343
00:16:10,133 --> 00:16:11,600
<c.Japanese>（せきばらい）</c.Japanese>

344
